title: Manuel d'oncologie - G. Roussy
description:
Gustave Roussy (Villejuif, France), the first center of fight against cancer in Europe, offers his view toolkit oncology supportive care Gustave Roussy to use internal (physicians, surgeons, anesthesiologists and intensivists) .

You will find in this application:
- The full manual (procedures, diagnostic and therapeutic proposals, etc.).
- Access by chapters or pathologies
- Frequent calculations
- The media (images, movies, documents)
- Practical information for internal Gustave Roussy

Important:
The use of this application is for health professionals.
